data.description: Welcome to 817 Stawell Dr in Patterson! This stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a true gem and was built in 2020. With tall ceilings and an open concept design, it's a breath of fresh air. The kitchen boasts a large island with a sink, good sized pantry and modern charm. Step outside to your covered patio, perfect for entertaining. Plus, enjoy the convenience of a water softener system. Close to shopping, schools, and freeways, your dream home awaits!
